cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a novel attention framework for improving image classification accuracy, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of Long Short Term Memory (LSTM) in the proposed framework suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the regularization ability of the proposed framework, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
